snippet.title: SSX | E3 2011 Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Fresh from EA's Conference at E3 2011, Defy Reality and Own The Planet in this all-new SSX Cinematic trailer. You may also spot a freshly unveiled, yet familiar face in the SSX roster..

SSX hits the slopes in January 2012 - for more info, visit http://www.ea.com/uk/ssx
